UMI is a decentralized blockchain platform with an open source code. A high throughput capacity of 65,535 TPS and an improved PoA consensus algorithm make our transactions instant, completely free and safe. UMI has the fastest blockchain in the world.

With our official extension, the entire UMI ecosystems is always at your finger tips:

• Create and manage your UMI wallet;
• Send and receive UMI coins and tokens based on the UMI blockchain;
• Review transaction history;
• Sign your messages;
• Interact with the UMI OneApp ecosystem

UMI is developing a unique ecosystem — UMI OneApp — that will become a universe of DeFi solutions in a single app. UMI OneApp users will have access to absolutely all DeFi tools and to almost all cryptocurrencies and tokens available on the market.

UMI Wallet extension is all the functionality you need in your browser. It’s fast, safe, and easy to use. Welcome to the future!
